  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_390f4cc8e355af0c04e851e56cfdb1d6">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>About 588 travel views from around the world, including North America and Europe, by many well-known early travel photographers such as Francis Frith, James Valentine, George Washington Wilson and Carlo Ponti.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <separatedmaterial audience="internal" id="aspace_430b76c1265d2d871d034edb58ab02f5">
    <head>Separated Materials</head>
<p>Two volumes of Erskine Beveridge's Wanderings with a Camera (1922) as well as 11 photograph albums featuring views of Scotland, France, Belgium, Wales, England and the Netherlands cataloged separately.</p>  </separatedmaterial>
